==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Desirefulness
<hw>De*sire"ful*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being
desireful; eagerness to obtain and possess.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>desirefulness</qex> of our minds much augmenteth and
increaseth our pleasure.</q> <rj><qau>Udall.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Desireless</ent>⟦br⟧
